Package org.melior.server.smpp

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SmppListener
    Implements an easy to use, auto-configuring SMPP listener which listens for messages and receipts and processes any new messages and receipts that arrive.
    SmppListenerBuilder
    Convenience class for building an SmppListener.
    SmppListenerConfig
    Configuration parameters for an SmppListener, with defaults.
    SmppReceipt
    An SMPP delivery receipt.
